module REQ_HA_DASHBOARD_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-HA-DASHBOARD-01
 * Title       : Real-time Patient Dashboard
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
